  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large clay tagine or Dutch oven over medium low heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until caramelized, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the grated ginger and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, paprika, and cayenne pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the doenjang and shio-koji cure. Cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chickpeas and cook for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Cover the tagine and transfer to the oven. Cook at 300°F (150°C) for 2 hours.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley and lemon wedges."
